channel.title: How To Get My Server To Run
channel.description:
Please help me get my server to run. I've been trying to get it to run for about a week now. By the way I downloaded the server, which can be the problem. When I click Run-Server, it says its online, but when I try my ip-address it won't let me log in. The ip is Blitzkingdom.no-ip.biz. If you know the problem, and can get it to run properly, i'll give you admin. =)
P.S. My aim screen name is "John Podzinski"

Try Compiling Server and try editing in a command and it might start up
Or you might have a Server that is trying to delete your windows stuff
Make sure no files have del.windows in them or anything such as that
